    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "\"dangerous gamble\" sounds pretty strong lol. but think about it, if you keep borrowing more money to pay for social programs, aren't you just passing a massive bill to the next generation? isnt it actually more \"immoral\" to leave kids with a bankrupt country just so we can maintain certain services today? shouldn't the most ethical thing be to fix the books first?",
